{"tid":686253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好萊塢男星萊恩·雷諾斯慘死於家中，疑似仇殺","createTime":"2018-06-01T05:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T06:45:57.000Z","uid":81094,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab38cc4c66172f8dc90a28f2f15d490c067e53a","tid":686253,"uid":81094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"【新聞快報】<br />\n根據福斯新聞外電報導，好萊塢男星萊恩&middot;雷諾斯昨（30）日於家中身亡。<br />\n加州警方發表聲明，這位曾獲《時人雜誌》選為2010年全球最性感男人的新星，頭部中彈死於他的桌旁，桌上放著他即將主演的超級英雄新片《綠光戰警》劇本。<br />\n<br />\n加州警方目前尚未證實為自殺或謀殺，但已掌握一位身穿紅色緊身衣的嫌疑人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/134933_6ea9d106b00705453f9df96399d2bce4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F134933_6ea9d106b00705453f9df96399d2bce4.png&h=774aa966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jackal.lin/posts/10156432048653436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjackal.lin%2Fposts%2F10156432048653436&d=N%2BywAU3rtOvD%2FF0MpcDFviwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0012ede1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jackal.lin/posts/10156432048653436</a>"},{"pid":"7fec83d3a2891de14735201d655f624eda355ef6","tid":686253,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"462229d61e9ca5e7bd6fbf55bccbcf5d0ed76cac","tid":686253,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nerdist.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/avengers_black_widow-black-widow-is-confirmed-for-battle-in-civil-war-jpeg-224673-970x545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnerdist.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Favengers_black_widow-black-widow-is-confirmed-for-battle-in-civil-war-jpeg-224673-970x545.jpg&h=737ff8f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b68d4b3898eeff3cdc7f7574fb12b2300397ac39","tid":686253,"uid